	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" ><br /> I'm no wizard....but some of the characters in the story are, especially one rather well known to these boards...this tale I have been writing over the past year for the Vazaelle community..It's rather long...it's not edited...but it is finished...I'll post it in pieces here...hope you enjoy...=) <br /></font></p>
	
